OL,3,CCritical incident declared at
OL,4,CNottingham hospitals after
OL,5,C"significant pressures"
OL,7,FA critical incident has been declared
OL,8,Fat two Nottingham hospitals following
OL,9,F"significant pressures" on services.
OL,11,FStaff at Queens' Medical Centre and
OL,12,FNottingham City Hospital are working
OL,13,Funder "extreme pressure" with high
OL,14,Fdemands and long patient waiting
OL,15,Ftimes, particularly in the A&E.
OL,17,FThis follows a critical incident that
OL,18,Fwas declared earlier in January, with
OL,19,Frising demand, winter infections and
OL,20,Fstaff sickness which led to delays in
OL,21,Fservices.
