OL,5,C"significant pressures"
OL,7,FThere has been a significant increase
OL,8,Fin patients presenting with
OL,9,Frespiratory issues at the hospitals,
OL,10,Fwhich is causing capacity pressures in
OL,11,FA&E and on wards.
OL,13,FPatients are having "unacceptable and
OL,14,Flengthy waits" on corridors in A&E,
OL,15,Fwith a high number of respiratory
OL,16,Fpatients awaiting care.
