OL,3,CCritical incident declared at
OL,4,CNottingham hospitals after
OL,5,C"significant pressures"
OL,7,FAndrew Hall, Chief Operating Officer
OL,8,Fat Nottingham University Hospitals NHS
OL,9,FTrust, said: "The pressures we are
OL,10,Fseeing in our hospitals are
OL,11,Fsignificant and our patients are
OL,12,Fhaving to wait longer than they should
OL,13,Fto be seen.
OL,15,F"We have been working tirelessly all
OL,16,Fweek to mitigate the pressures we are
OL,17,Fcurrently seeing but this has not had
OL,18,Fthe desired impact, and so we
OL,19,Fdeclaring a Critical Incident is
OL,20,Fnecessary to protect patient safety.
OL,26,@qD@NOUwD@AOU
