OL,4,CNottingham hospitals after
OL,5,C"significant pressures"
OL,7,F"I would like to apologise to all
OL,8,Fpatients who are in our hospitals and
OL,9,Fare waiting for long periods.
OL,11,F"While staff are doing all they can to
OL,12,Fhelp people to be seen quickly and
OL,13,Fhope to have more than 200 patients
OL,14,Fhome today, we also need the public to
OL,15,Fhelp us. Getting patients home as soon
OL,16,Fas they are well enough to is vital
OL,17,Fand we would like families and carers
OL,18,Fto please prioritise getting their
OL,19,Floved ones home when they are
OL,20,Fcontacted.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOU
