OL,7,F"This could mean collecting them
OL,8,Fbefore you are due to finish work,
OL,9,Fmaking sure they have their medication
OL,10,Fready at home and ensuring they have
OL,11,Fsomewhere warm to go back to.
OL,13,F"Please also consider carefully
OL,14,Fwhether or not you need to attend A&E.
OL,15,FIf you are in an emergency situation,
OL,16,Fplease still attend. Otherwise,
OL,17,Fconsider if there are other services
OL,18,Fthat could help ` your local pharmacy,
OL,19,For calling 111 for advice.
