OL,7,F"If you do have an appointment booked
OL,8,Fwith us, please do still attend until
OL,9,Ftold otherwise."
OL,11,FThe NUH say they are addressing
OL,12,Fpressures on the hospitals by creating
OL,13,Fmore bed space for patients, with
OL,14,Fstaff asked to take on additional
OL,15,Fshifts to facilitate the increase in
OL,16,Fpatient demands.
OL,18,FStaff are working hard to identify
OL,19,Fopportunities to discharge patients as
OL,20,Fquickly and safely as possible.
